tyle="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><strong><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:16px">BẢO QUẢN:</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:16px">Để nơi kh&ocirc; tho&aacute;ng, tr&aacute;nh &aacute;nh nắng trực tiếp. Để xa tầm tay trẻ em.</span></span></p>\r\n', '', '', 'BODY', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'kem-body-whitening-body-lotion-cream', 'Kem Body Whitening Body Lotion Cream', '', ''),
